This is the Power Menu Mod the Sammsung Epic 4G EL30 ROM

It adds reboot and reboot to recovery to the power menu. It based on an excellent
guide by xda-developers.com user untermensch for the Samsung Vibrant.

See the commits on the original EI22 port for details on bugfixes and enhancements
to the original mod.

Original EI22 Port can be found here:
https://github.com/toadlife/EI22-Power-Menu-Mod

Credits:

* untermensch  - Original guide for the Samsung Vibrant
* toadlife - Original port to the Epic (EI22) plus fixes and enhancements.